475
00:29:32,039 --> 00:29:32,819
[SPEAKER_00] te svoje emocije.

476
00:29:32,819 --> 00:29:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da vjernici svakako mogu koristiti,

477
00:29:35,119 --> 00:29:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] znači, ono, očeva, ljubav, Isus,

478
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:39,200
[SPEAKER_00] znači, bilo ko s neba,

479
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] s kim smo bliski.

480
00:29:40,039 --> 00:29:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] Imam jednu klijenticu koja je prošla

481
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:43,180
[SPEAKER_00] nekakva traumatska iskustva

482
00:29:43,180 --> 00:29:45,299
