[SPEAKER_00] kad smo, ne znam,

492
00:30:01,099 --> 00:30:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] na primjer, bojite se pa ste dobili batine

493
00:30:02,980 --> 00:30:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] kod dijete.

494
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:06,640
[SPEAKER_00] Teško je to sad nekad sam sa sobom se.

495
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:07,220
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

496
00:30:07,220 --> 00:30:08,220
[SPEAKER_00] Pa se možemo tako.

497
00:30:08,220 --> 00:30:09,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam znam da sam nju pitala,

498
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:10,440
[SPEAKER_00] ok, zamisli boga, otca.

499
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] On je pun ljubavi.

500
00:30:11,380 --> 00:30:12,140
[SPEAKER_00] On te stvorio.

501
00:30:12,140 --> 00:30:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] Šta bi on rekao kad,

502
00:30:13,559 --> 00:30:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] evo, ti si ugužvi i sad strah?

503
00:30:15,779 --> 00:30:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jel, bi rekao,

504
00:30:16,420 --> 00:30:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] joj, kak te tak strah?

505
00:30:17,619 --> 00:30:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] Kaj se tu, ono,

506
00:30:18,740 --> 00:30:21,339
[SPEAKER_00] bez veze filozofiraš?

507
00:30:21,339 --> 00:30:23,299
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne bi nikad to tako rekao.

508
00:30:23,299 --> 00:30:25,200
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nekad je baš izazov

509
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,660
[SPEAKER_00] dobiti suosjećanja za sebe

510
00:30:26,660 --> 00:30:27,559
[SPEAKER_00] jer ga nismo imali.

511
00:30:27,559 --> 00:30:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

512
00:30:28,099 --> 00:30:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] I tu se vraćam opet na ovo sa djecom.

513
00:30:29,940 --> 00:30:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ispravna reakcija,

514
00:30:31,059 --> 00:30:31,880
