520
00:30:38,759 --> 00:30:40,359
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćeš naučiti to suosjećanje.

521
00:30:40,359 --> 00:30:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali baš je.

522
00:30:40,920 --> 00:30:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, umiriti,

523
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] znači neki način da si smiriš tijelo,

524
00:30:43,779 --> 00:30:45,339
