530
00:30:50,660 --> 00:30:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] ali rješenje je u smislu

531
00:30:51,599 --> 00:30:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] strateški si posložit.

532
00:30:53,380 --> 00:30:54,319
[SPEAKER_00] To može, na primjer,

533
00:30:54,319 --> 00:30:55,099
