537
00:30:59,140 --> 00:31:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, znam Mirjanu,

538
00:31:00,460 --> 00:31:01,140
[SPEAKER_00] ona mi je super,

539
00:31:01,140 --> 00:31:02,299
