540
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:03,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, nikad nisam bila ovdje,

541
00:31:03,740 --> 00:31:04,779
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam jako znateđena,

542
00:31:04,779 --> 00:31:05,640
