545
00:31:08,140 --> 00:31:09,759
[SPEAKER_00] neko rješenje kako si olakšati.

546
00:31:09,759 --> 00:31:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] I završeno je da

547
00:31:11,420 --> 00:31:12,920
