551
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ne uspijemo,

552
00:31:18,099 --> 00:31:18,700
[SPEAKER_00] isto, ok,

553
00:31:18,700 --> 00:31:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj put nisam uspjela,

554
00:31:19,880 --> 00:31:21,279
[SPEAKER_00] onda idemo još jednom.

555
00:31:21,279 --> 00:31:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, ovo jako zvuči prozaječno,

556
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] to su sad neka četiri koraka.

557
00:31:24,980 --> 00:31:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] U terapiji imamo terapeute

558
