584
00:31:55,819 --> 00:31:57,420
[SPEAKER_01] A kasnije postane automacija.

585
00:31:57,420 --> 00:31:58,599
[SPEAKER_01] Da, apsolutno.

586
00:31:58,599 --> 00:31:59,019
[SPEAKER_01] Super.

587
00:31:59,019 --> 00:32:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] I super mi je ovo

588
